<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  <title>Pet Shelter Portal</title>
  <style>
    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(155deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-primary-dark) 55%, #a8452c 100%);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 5.5rem 1.5rem 6.5rem;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .hero::before {
      content: "🐾";
      position: absolute;
      font-size: 18rem;
      opacity: 0.08;
      left: -3rem;
      top: -3rem;
      transform: rotate(15deg);
    }
    .hero::after {
      content: "🐾";
      position: absolute;
      font-size: 18rem;
      opacity: 0.08;
      right: -3rem;
      bottom: -5rem;
      transform: rotate(-20deg);
    }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 2.9rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; position: relative; }
    .hero p.lead { font-size: 1.15rem; opacity: 0.92; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; position: relative; }
    .hero .btn-light { border-radius: 0.9rem; font-weight: 800; padding: 0.75rem 2rem; }
    .steps-section { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
    .step-card {
      background: var(--color-surface);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
      height: 100%;
    }
    .step-card .step-icon {
      width: 56px; height: 56px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--color-bg);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      margin: 0 auto 1rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('header') %>

  <div class="hero">
    <h1>Every pet deserves a<br>loving home.</h1>
    <p class="lead">Browse rescued dogs, cats, and other animals looking for their forever family — and give one of them a second chance at happiness.</p>
    <% if (user) { %>
      <a href="/pets" class="btn btn-light btn-lg">Start Browsing Pets</a>
    <% } else { %>
      <a href="/register" class="btn btn-light btn-lg">Get Started</a>
    <% } %>
  </div>

  <div class="container steps-section">
    <div class="row g-4">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-icon">🔍</div>
          <h5>1. Browse &amp; Favourite</h5>
          <p class="text-muted mb-0">Search by species, age, and temperament to find a pet that fits your lifestyle.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-icon">📝</div>
          <h5>2. Apply to Adopt</h5>
          <p class="text-muted mb-0">Submit a short application so our shelter team can get to know you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-icon">🏡</div>
          <h5>3. Bring Them Home</h5>
          <p class="text-muted mb-0">Get notified the moment you're approved, and welcome your new best friend.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
